data.description: POTENTIAL SHORT SALE, SUBJECT TO BANK APPROVAL.Discover a gorgeous 3 Bedroom/1 Bathroom home, recently remodeled and situated in an upcoming area of Deland, complete with convenient proximity to Stadium. The tasteful remodel consists of a new kitchen, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. You'll also have the added benefit of a Bonus Room that can easily be used as an office or extra bedroom with new flooring . 2023 Roof and newer AC and water heater make this home modern and efficient. An inviting remodeled bathroom completes this amazing home! Make sure to schedule your showing today and submit your offer for your chance to make this dream home yours!
